  m_Name: LoopReflect_01
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ReflectBranch
  lines:
  - Okay, Luke. It's now or never.
  - She's right there.
  - Today is the day. No more chickening out.
  - You're gonna ask Daisy to the homecoming dance.
  - And if you don't ask her this passing period, Brett Kissenger is gonna ask her.
  - And they'll get married.
  - And you'll die alone.
  - "Just need to figure out what to say to her\u2026.."
  commitLines:
  - Only 3 minutes left in passing period.
  - "It\u2019s go time."
  - Deep Breath.
  - You can do this.
